According to him, the scientific center is carrying out work on supersonic topics both within the framework of international consortia and cooperation with the Ministry of Trade.
“We feel it will take us two to three years to get a technology demonstrator, as well as another 10-15 years to get a serial machine that allows to carry out transportation in our homeland,” added Spialo.
