News.Ru: Users: Facebook works with crashes
According to the tracking of the popular Internet resources of the Downdetecor service, in some countries users have problems related to the functioning of the social network Facebook.
They emerged from midnight on Sunday, September 30, in Moscow time.
In the United States, Brazil, the United Kingdom, Denmark, the Netherlands and Germany, users complain about the difficulty of authorization (51 percent), that the social network is not working (36 percent), and that images are not uploaded (11 percent), TASS reports.
Last Friday, social network representatives said they had discovered a security issue on Facebook that affected nearly 50 million accounts, according to the report.
